                            <comment id="15307934" author="tgraves" created="Tue, 31 May 2016 15:39:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I should have a patch up for this shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15310312" author="tgraves" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2016 13:36:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-15659&quot; title=&quot;Ensure FileSystem is gotten from path in InMemoryCatalog&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-15659&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-15659&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15310487" author="tgraves" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2016 15:34:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note the performance impact is in the 10&apos;s of minutes with large # of partitions.  With the change to pickBin reverted it takes about 10 seconds.  For now I think we revert it and we can look at possible other optimizations later.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
